{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"14":"Fasting (Kitab Al-Siyam)"},"section_detail":{"14":{"hadithnumber_first":2313,"hadithnumber_last":2476,"arabicnumber_first":2313,"arabicnumber_last":2476}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2466,"arabicnumber":2466,"text":"Abu Huraira رضي الله عنه a dit : Le Prophète ﷺ faisait l’i’tikaf pendant dix jours de Ramadan chaque année. Mais l’année où il est décédé, il a fait l’i’tikaf pendant vingt jours","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (2044)"}],"reference":{"book":14,"hadith":154}}]}